headline: How Analysts See UnitedHealth’s Story Shifting Amid Fresh Optimism and Ongoing Challenges
summary: UnitedHealth Group’s stock has seen its consensus analyst price target edge up from $352.21 to $360.84, a move that reflects a cautiously growing optimism around its future prospects. This recent adjustment highlights how improvements in Medicare Advantage ratings and increased earnings visibility are bolstering confidence, even as some challenges linger.
